{"tid":371234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"遠在我的眼前 近在我的心","createTime":"2017-08-23T14:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T00:48:38.000Z","uid":19800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff281aa159c2c45e0506688fadef8c0c386ca30e","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"尋覓你的眼神 期待你聲音<br />\n人間煙火 何等污染<br />\n誰能做天使護蔭<br />\n<br />\n文字再多 寫不出我的愛<br />\n風花雪月中 少不了 無盡等待<br />\n年月更多 一生一世煉成的愛<br />\n跌入這首歌 唱盡了多少感慨<br />\n<br />\n世上有些愛情 註定要發生<br />\n途上有一個人 難讓我安枕<br />\n長相廝守 無須擁有<br />\n平行著不要步近<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單戀好撚辛苦啊屌你老母<br />\n好掛住佢 但係再搵佢都唔會有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735463252b2cd8b7716b9ea35ac14b616114e431","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9670cc4bf97bdf524649fe0b308440977b18eb55","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7669db4883cb50c76cf3e6b5f1c3121dc1f24fc2","tid":371234,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"Hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e94059aaa3d4e00897a6eb6961c830df103acd","tid":371234,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5657bd977ca8a212b7980510f15c9ebd509aedbf","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"圍爐吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffbe0684732f93140a744fce576309973670aae","tid":371234,"uid":134295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"明知對方唔會中意自己 但都係要手賤去搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只求繼續留係佢身邊 直到佢搵到屬於佢既幸福為止"},{"pid":"413b0c1322bd2e281c1ec723f4af752112295eea","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知對方唔會中意自己 但都係要手賤去搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只求繼續留係佢身邊 直到佢搵到屬於佢既幸福為止</blockquote><br />\n我已經放棄左 唔再主動搵佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留返幾分面子比自己算"},{"pid":"da74fcf53adc8daf631b7101466c21e67c39edbe","tid":371234,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:48:38.000Z","msg":"無撚用<br />\n又再好掛住佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}